details.text: The URL should refer directly to the ImplementationGuide resource (e.g. include '/ImplementationGuide/')
The canonical URL http://hl7.eu/fhir/extensions doesn't point to an actual ImplementationGuide resource

The extension http://hl7.org/fhir/5.0/StructureDefinition/extension-BodyStructure.includedStructure.laterality from FHIR version 5.0 is not allowed to be used at this point (this element is [BodyStructure]; allowed for this version = e:BodyStructure.includedStructure; this is a warning since contexts may be renamed between FHIR versions)
